      <tr><td>full refresh (10-15 yr)</td><td>$800 – $1,200</td><td>Gasket + sensor + valve + cleaning</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/brands/viking-refrigerator-repair/">Viking refrigerator repair</a> · <a href="/brands/viking-stove-repair/">Viking stove repair</a> · <a href="/brands/viking-range-repair/">Viking range repair</a> · <a href="/brands/viking-ice-maker-repair/">Viking ice maker repair</a> · <a href="/services/built-in-refrigerator-repair/">Built-in refrigerator service hub</a>.</p>
